### Get All Attributes
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/attributes/all
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Attribute by ID
@attributeId = REPLACE_WITH_ACTUAL_ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/attributes/{{attributeId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update Attribute
PUT {{baseUrl}}/products/attributes/{{attributeId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Updated color options for products",
  "displayOrder": 10
}

### Delete Attribute
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/products/attributes/{{attributeId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
